      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Be One with the Bow",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nSpeed, agility, and positioning\r\nare the signatures of the \u003CCOL RED\u003ETobi-\r\nKadachi\u003C/COL\u003E. Have you ever noticed\r\nhow similar they are to the bow?\r\nWell, now you know, go see it\r\nfor yourself!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Apprivoiser l\u0027arc",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique ! Vitesse,\r\nagilit\u00E9, positionnement, c\u0027est\r\ntout \u00E7a le \u003CCOL RED\u003ETobi-Kadachi\u003C/COL\u003E.\r\n\u00C7a ressemble aux qualit\u00E9s requises\r\npour utiliser un arc. Tu vois\r\nce que je veux dire ?",
        "Target": "Chasser deux Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Domina l\u0027arco",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "OK, \u00E8 ora di imparare:\r\nvelocit\u00E0, agilit\u00E0 e posizione\r\nsono i segni distintivi del\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003ETobi-Kadachi\u003C/COL\u003E. Hai mai notato\r\nquanto sono simili all\u0027arco?\r\nOra che lo sai, vai a vedere\r\ncon i tuoi occhi!",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Beherrschung des Bogens",
        "Client": "Meister Utsushi",
        "Description": "Okay, Ass, aufgepasst! Einen\r\n\u003CCOLS RED\u003ETobi-Kadachi\u003C/COL\u003E zeichnen Tempo,\r\nAgilit\u00E4t und Positionierung\r\naus. Ist dir aufgefallen, dass\r\nes sich mit dem Bogen genauso\r\nverh\u00E4lt? Na, jetzt kannst du\r\ndich selbst \u00FCberzeugen!",
        "Target": "Erjage zwei Tobi-Kadachi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Sintoniza con el arco",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "Hacha, \u00A1hora de aprender!\r\nVelocidad, agilidad y atacar\r\ndesde arriba es el secreto del\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003ETobi-Kadachi\u003C/COL\u003E. \u00BFTe has dado\r\ncuenta de lo parecido que es\r\nal arco? Bien, ahora lo sabes,\r\n\u00A1ve a comprobarlo!",
        "Target": "Caza 2 Tobi-Kadachi",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
